nodes.text: Subterrel sector was a sector in the Outer Rim Territories, between the Rimma Trade Route and the Hydian Way. Planets in the sector included Subterrel itself, Fwatna, Kallidah, Orax and Polis Massa.
The sector neither was part of the Galactic Republic at the time of its collapse, nor of the Galactic Empire during the Reconquest of the Rim. However, it was annexed by the Empire prior to 0 ABY.
